{"tid":1302623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"很多人以為，香港獨立的話，他需要大量陸軍守住邊界去抵禦陸侵，建立一支防守型軍隊。這是錯誤的。","createTime":"2019-07-10T04:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T20:10:19.000Z","uid":8543,"like":86,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"61640484de9334824afdfe290a750ee92e6755da","tid":1302623,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"Cheng Lap<br />\n<br />\n很多人以為，香港獨立的話，他需要大量陸軍守住邊界去抵禦陸侵，建立一支防守型軍隊。這是錯誤的。遇上陸上攻擊，香港有需要時應拖延和撤離主要機能，將軍隊化整為零，迅速融入社會中，警察和公務系統可主動跟佔領者合作。反正佔領者也不得不接受他們運作。<br />\n<br />\n香港縱深太小，防守型軍隊沒意義。應該在各國租借軍事基地，建立一支反攻復國以及長期牽制用的軍隊，主要目標是以海外軍事行動打擊侵略方在海外的經濟設施，航線及盟友，以及輔助盟友進行情報作戰，策反與反間諜。<br />\n<br />\n陸上作戰部隊由少量具高度外交能力的骨幹組成。他們大部分時間都是作為更大載體的種子。<br />\n<br />\n第一，他們能夠回香港裝成平民策動遊擊活動，在地破壞經濟與統治架構，或牽制本地公務體系消極配合佔領。<br />\n<br />\n第二，如果需要短期的大兵力，應該使用現成的傭兵，可從南亞臺灣或非洲僱用，由本地團隊配合協調任務和衡量合約執行情況。預算自然一早搬去海外，政府機能也要能離岸運作。<br />\n<br />\n因此香港適合一支資訊作戰能力優秀的攻擊輔助型軍隊，邊境守備交給警察做。他們的命令就是和平地妨礙外國軍隊進入，拖延時間。反正打不贏，但可以拖。<br />\n<br />\n香港人不需要拘泥於國共的大陸軍思維，本來香港自古以來地理上都是海盜基地，海盜從不以陸軍防守的。"},{"pid":"06d587abd1a22777e0b2e3c1dba6ba8a744917c4","tid":1302623,"uid":234596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Navy ?"},{"pid":"6ce8d8cf546754c0ad5e9031bf0d0d49eee4e0ee","tid":1302623,"uid":43141,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:41:25.000Z","msg":"免費租昂船洲畀美軍咪得lor"},{"pid":"d747ee0a9d3933626e2e818750ffb7f3c9c8b208","tid":1302623,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06d587abd1a22777e0b2e3c1dba6ba8a744917c4","tid":1302623,"uid":234596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Navy ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Corps"},{"pid":"f7da7a7f4100c0d132e2d8fa65f01c4d35aa9ae7","tid":1302623,"uid":44646,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:49:16.000Z","msg":"鄭立有好多時太理想化<br />\n<br />\n全香港都係海盜的話，的確不需防守<br />\n但一般香港人呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果侵略者以「叛國」起訴留在香港的重要人物<br />\n香港防衛軍要唔要返來？<br />\n<br />\n(另外，唔知點解，大家假設香港獨立成功，<br />\n仍然係一個780萬人的金融中心？<br />\n而且國民都支持獨立<br />\n呢個假設同現實差距實在太遠)"},{"pid":"e7e31295030dbddd05f96db8aa7b60615c40c5d9","tid":1302623,"uid":164442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"7.10 - TVB港姐 - <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1300556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1300556</a><br />\n7.10 - 麥小姐追思會 ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30<br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8ChV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=06660227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8ChV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=c65eb926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - 光復港大 守衛我城 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2S6Lw1T&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8ChV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=03439174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T</a><br />\n7.13 - 光復上水 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/32eEvRm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32eEvRm&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8ChV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=a60321f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/32eEvRm</a><br />\n7.14 - 沙田區大遊行 - <a href=\"http://t.me/st7142019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fst7142019&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8ChV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=f411c48a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/st7142019</a><br />\n7.28 - 將軍澳遊行 - <a href=\"http://t.me/tko728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftko728&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8ChV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=47815221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/tko728</a><br />\n隨時 - 抵制TVB - <a href=\"http://t.me/noTVBteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVBteam&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8ChV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=30afe4a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/noTVBteam</a><br />\n隨時 - 美國聯署 人權民主法案 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOf0aj&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8ChV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=e698a12e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">撤回修例 收回暴動 撤銷控罪 追究警隊 雙真普選<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰，不分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有信用評分之後 痴memo 遊行 上網講錯嘢 信錯教都可能扣你分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請不要再裝睡 行動吧香港人</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上水遊行路線更新</span></strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1302535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1302535</a>"},{"pid":"59d32d6c2386bb492a859114a0d449ed01449be9","tid":1302623,"uid":24615,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"所以話香港需要更大既生存空間 <br />\n應該係全大灣區/廣東"},{"pid":"cbd93ed715c5cfdfdf4943d21ec431158c33caf3","tid":1302623,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba136dd20403994a0b9d92a5c36c3d40c8caca4f","tid":1302623,"uid":115096,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"假設香港獨立下情況<br />\n講下軍事局勢分析<br />\n今日軍事上情況已經同80年代完全唔同<br />\n中國與香港其實存在博弈<br />\n唔係話解放軍有幾多人幾多飛機導彈<br />\n80年代深圳廣州基本上係冇經濟價值<br />\n一旦開戰... 香港係唯一受害者<br />\n但今日深圳人口經濟價值<br />\n再加上廣東有大約十座核電廠<br />\n而廣州係供獻中國四成GDP<br />\n七成外匯經香港流向中國<br />\n中國已經冇可能承受南方全面戰<br />\n咁其實唔需點要防守<br />\n總之講明一見地面部隊或海軍搶灘<br />\n就會射導彈去深交所、核電廠<br />\n齊齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁永遠只會兩邊鬥屌唔會開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ff984ee1b5bf111a0cff6c3d8b42b7c5b5054f","tid":1302623,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba136dd20403994a0b9d92a5c36c3d40c8caca4f","tid":1302623,"uid":115096,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"假設香港獨立下情況<br />\n講下軍事局勢分析<br />\n今日軍事上情況已經同80年代完全唔同<br />\n中國與香港其實存在博弈<br />\n唔係話解放軍有幾多人幾多飛機導彈<br />\n80年代深圳廣州基本上係冇經濟價值<br />\n一旦開戰... 香港係唯一受害者<br />\n但今日深圳人口經濟價值<br />\n再加上廣東有大約十座核電廠<br />\n而廣州係供獻中國四成GDP<br />\n七成外匯經香港流向中國<br />\n中國已經冇可能承受南方全面戰<br />\n咁其實唔需點要防守<br />\n總之講明一見地面部隊或海軍搶灘<br />\n就會射導彈去深交所、核電廠<br />\n齊齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁永遠只會兩邊鬥屌唔會開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"所以香港係要Mossad<br />\n而唔係IDF"},{"pid":"c3f9e9c717bac6c0bb156d6f30da45bdc6d1914e","tid":1302623,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59d32d6c2386bb492a859114a0d449ed01449be9","tid":1302623,"uid":24615,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"所以話香港需要更大既生存空間 <br />\n應該係全大灣區/廣東"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:27:27.000Z","msg":"用錢買？"},{"pid":"d5c3c25c2aaaa4c923d8b4f1b725832960607138","tid":1302623,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"紙上談獨 最現實一定係美國駐軍"},{"pid":"a7785a893208379e808c8b30fa608161925407bc","tid":1302623,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:31:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>反大灣區一國一制融合 !!!</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由小處到大局，逃犯條例的真面目。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1228296/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1228296/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span st